<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GRASSROOTS MEDIA - Radio/Audio Insertion Order</title>
    <style>
        @page { 
            size: 8.5in 11in; 
            margin: 0.75in; 
            orphans: 3;
            widows: 3;
        }
        
        body { 
            font-family: 'Arial', 'Helvetica', sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.3; 
            color: #000000; 
            background: #ffffff; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            font-size: 11pt;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .document-container { 
            background: #ffffff; 
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 7in;
            margin: 0 auto; 
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        .header-date {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 15pt;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .document-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20pt;
            padding-bottom: 10pt;
            border-bottom: 2pt solid #C3875B;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            page-break-after: avoid;
        }
        
        .document-title h1 {
            color: #000000;
            font-size: 16pt;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5pt;
        }
        
        .order-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20pt;
            padding: 10pt;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 3pt;
            border-left: 3pt solid #C3875B;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .order-number, .order-date {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        
        /* Parallel contact sections optimized for print */
        .contact-sections {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20pt;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .contact-sections .section {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 48%;
            vertical-align: top;
            padding-right: 4%;
        }
        
        .contact-sections .section:last-child {
            padding-right: 0;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 15pt;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 8pt 12pt;
            margin: 0 0 10pt 0;
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #000000;
            border-left: 3pt solid #C3875B;
            page-break-after: avoid;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .section-content {
            padding: 0 12pt;
        }
        
        .contact-info p {
            margin: 3pt 0;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .contact-info a {
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        /* Improved placement details for print */
        .placement-details-container {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 12pt;
            border-radius: 3pt;
            margin-bottom: 15pt;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .details-grid {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 10pt;
        }
        
        .details-row {
            display: table-row;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: table-cell;
            padding: 3pt 12pt 3pt 0;
            width: 48%;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        
        .details-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #C3875B;
            font-size: 9pt;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.3pt;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 2pt;
        }
        
        .details-value {
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #000000;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .insertion-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 10pt 0;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1pt solid #cccccc;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }
        
        .insertion-table th {
            background: #C3875B;
            color: white;
            padding: 6pt 4pt;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 8pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.3pt;
            border: 1pt solid #ffffff;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .insertion-table td {
            padding: 6pt 4pt;
            text-align: center;
            border: 0.5pt solid #dddddd;
            font-size: 9pt;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        
        .insertion-table tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .total-cost {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 12pt;
            margin: 10pt 0;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 10pt;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 3pt;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .total-cost span {
            color: #C3875B;
        }
        
        /* Parallel information sections for print */
        .info-sections {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 15pt;
        }
        
        .info-section {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 48%;
            padding-right: 4%;
            vertical-align: top;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1pt solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 3pt;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .info-section:last-child {
            padding-right: 0;
        }
        
        .info-section .section-title {
            margin: 0;
            border-radius: 0;
            border-left: none;
            background: #C3875B;
            color: white;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .info-section .section-content {
            padding: 10pt;
        }
        
        .terms-list {
            padding-left: 15pt;
            margin: 8pt 0;
        }
        
        .terms-list li {
            margin-bottom: 6pt;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 20pt;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 12pt;
            border-radius: 3pt;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
        
        .signature-grid {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 15pt 0;
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 48%;
            padding-right: 4%;
            margin: 15pt 0;
        }
        
        .signature-line:last-child {
            padding-right: 0;
        }
        
        .signature-line strong {
            display: block;
            border-top: none;
            padding-top: 5pt;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }
        
        .signature-line em {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #333333;
        }
        
        .signature-line small {
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #666666;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25pt;
            padding-top: 10pt;
            border-top: 1pt solid #cccccc;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #333333;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        /* Print-specific optimizations */
        @media print {
            body {
                font-size: 10pt;
                line-height: 1.2;
            }
            
            .document-container {
                padding: 0;
                max-width: 100%;
                width: 100%;
            }
            
            .contact-sections,
            .details-grid,
            .info-sections,
            .signature-grid {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
            
            .insertion-table {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
                font-size: 8pt;
            }
            
            .insertion-table th {
                font-size: 7pt;
            }
            
            .insertion-table td {
                font-size: 8pt;
                padding: 4pt 3pt;
            }
            
            .signature-section {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
                margin-top: 15pt;
            }
            
            .section {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                page-break-after: avoid;
            }
            
            /* Force colors in print */
            * {
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact !important;
                print-color-adjust: exact !important;
            }
        }
        
        /* Responsive fallback for screens */
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .contact-sections .section,
            .info-section,
            .signature-line,
            .detail-item {
                display: block;
                width: 100%;
                padding-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 10pt;
            }
            
            .contact-sections,
            .details-grid,
            .info-sections,
            .signature-grid {
                display: block;
            }
            
            .order-details {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 5pt;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="document-container">
        <div class="header-date">
            <div>{{formatDate (now) 'MM/DD/YYYY, h:mm A'}}</div>
            <div>Radio/Audio Insertion Order</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="document-title">
            <h1>GRASSROOTS MEDIA, LLC - RADIO/AUDIO INSERTION ORDER</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="order-details">
            <div class="order-number">
                <strong>Order Number:</strong> {{order_number}}
            </div>
            <div class="order-date">
                <strong>Date:</strong> {{original_order_date}}
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Parallel contact sections optimized for print -->
        <div class="contact-sections">
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">TO:</div>
                <div class="section-content contact-info">
                    <p><strong>{{'{{media_outlet_name}}'}}</strong></p>
                    <p>{{media_outlet_address}}</p>
                    <p>ATTN: {{full_name_from_media_outlet_contacts}}</p>
                    <p>Phone: {{phone_from_media_outlet_contacts}}</p>
                    <p>Email: {{email_from_media_outlet_contacts}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">FROM:</div>
                <div class="section-content contact-info">
                    <p><strong>Grassroots Media</strong></p>
                    <p>135 W 29th Street, Suite 302</p>
                    <p>New York, NY 10001</p>
                    <p><a href="https://www.grassrootsmedia.nyc">www.grassrootsmedia.nyc</a></p>
                    <p>Contact: {{account_executive_name}}</p>
                    <p>Phone: {{account_executive_phone}}</p>
                    <p>Email: {{account_executive_email}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Optimized placement details for print -->
        <div class="placement-details-container">
            <div class="section-title">PLACEMENT DETAILS</div>
            <div class="details-grid">
                <div class="details-row">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="details-label">Client:</div>
                        <div class="details-value">{{company_name_from_active_campaign}}</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="details-label">Campaign:</div>
                        <div class="details-value">{{campaign_title_from_active_campaign}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="details-row">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="details-label">Product/Service:</div>
                        <div class="details-value">{{product_or_service}}</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="details-label">Flight Dates:</div>
                        <div class="details-value">{{formatDate start_date_from_active_campaign 'MM/DD/YYYY'}} – {{formatDate end_date_from_active_campaign 'MM/DD/YYYY'}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">INSERTION SCHEDULE</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <table class="insertion-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                <th>Instructions</th>
                <th>Daypart</th>
                <th>Days</th>
                <th>Time of Day</th>
                <th>Spot Length</th>
                <th>Spots/Week</th>
                <th>Rate per Spot</th>
                <th>Total Spots</th>
                <th>Total Cost</th>
                <th>Script Provided</th>
                <th>Live Read</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each radio_media_placement_json_summary_rollup}}
                <tr>
                <td>{{special_instructions}}</td>
                <td>{{daypart}}</td>
                <td>{{days}}</td>
                <td>{{time_of_day}}</td>
                <td>{{spot_length}}</td>
                <td>{{spots_per_week}}</td>
                <td>${{currency rate_per_spot}}</td>
                <td>{{total_spots}}</td>
                <td>${{currency total_cost}}</td>
                <td>{{#if script_provided}}Yes{{else}}No{{/if}}</td>
                <td>{{#if live_read}}Yes{{else}}No{{/if}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/each}}
            </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="total-cost">
            <strong>TOTAL COST: <span>{{currency total_cost}}</span></strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Parallel information sections optimized for print -->
        <div class="info-sections">
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="section-title">TEARSHEET REQUIREMENTS</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <p>
                        Media outlet must provide one complimentary copy of the publication and an electronic tearsheet emailed to 
                        <a href="mailto:{{account_executive_email}}">{{account_executive_email}}</a> within 7 days of publication.
                        Grassroots Media cannot bill advertisers/clients until all tear sheets have been received.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="section-title">AD COPY</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <p>
                        Ad copy questions? Please contact <a href="mailto:{{account_executive_email}}">{{account_executive_email}}</a> 
                        or call {{production_contact_phone}}.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">TERMS & CONDITIONS</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <ul class="terms-list">
                    <li>Acknowledges Grassroots Media as its advertising agent and agrees to accept the net rate listed above.</li>
                    <li>Will not invoice the client or agency directly. Grassroots Media will make payment within 30 to 60 days of receiving the tear sheets and invoice.</li>
                    <li>Media outlet will hold all materials for possible future use.</li>
                    <li>Any changes to this insertion order must be approved in writing by Grassroots Media.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="signature-section">
            <div class="section-title">APPROVAL</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <p>Please check size, rate, and run date. Any changes must be approved by Grassroots Media prior to placement.</p>
                
                <!-- Parallel signature lines optimized for print -->
                <div class="signature-grid">
                    <div class="signature-line">
                        <strong>X_____________________________________</strong><br />
                        <em>Media Outlet Authorized Signature</em><br />
                        <small>Date: _____________</small>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="signature-line">
                        <strong>X_____________________________________</strong><br />
                        <em>Grassroots Media Authorized Signature</em><br />
                        <small>Date: _____________</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15pt;">
                    Please return signed copy to <a href="mailto:{{account_executive_email}}">{{account_executive_email}}</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Grassroots Media, LLC • Radio/Audio Insertion Order • Confidential Document</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>